] [經濟制裁TVB] 廣告商名單整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253538\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1253538</a><br />\n[經濟制裁無綫大行動] TVB廣告商list<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PjppuU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PjppuU</a></blockquote><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">整合咗廣告商list之後<br />\n我呼籲大家一齊展開行動<br />\n斷絶TVB米路！！！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRzF32T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRzF32T.png&h=8dd675be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正式展開攻擊</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1. Expedia+Trivago+<a href=\"http://Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHotels.com&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=852baea2\" target=\"_blank\">http://Hotels.com</a><br />\n2. HKTV Mall<br />\n3. 幸福傷風素</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>樓主根據呢幾個criteria去揀目標</strong><br />\n1. 重視online marketing<br />\n2. 多後生仔用，我地易動員<br />\n3. 夠普及，多香港人用<br />\n4. 有替代品<br />\n5. 知名品牌<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Quote自TVB 2018年annual report:</strong><br />\n<blockquote>「五大開支類別...奶粉穩佔開支第一位。第二大類別，貸款及按揭公司，護膚品類別穩佔第三位，第四 及第五大廣告開支客戶－旅行代理及醫療保健補充劑」</blockquote><br />\nExpedia屬於旅行代理；HKTV Mall有賣奶粉、護膚品、醫療保健補充劑，唔搞奶粉同貸款住係因為奶粉好難話轉就轉，貸款就少人用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>下面係揀呢3間野嘅原因：</strong><br />\n1. Expedia+Trivago+<a href=\"http://Hotels.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHotels.com&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=852baea2\" target=\"_blank\">http://Hotels.com</a>: 三間野同屬一個集團，之前搵達哥做代言人好明顯想吸引一班後生幫襯，如果連登呼籲佢唔喺TVB落廣告相信有一定影響力<br />\n2. HKTV Mall: 呢排士多俾人圍插，佢都食正條水，做本地人生意嘅更加應該同香港人同一陣線抵制TVB<br />\n3. 幸福傷風素： 呢幾年扮本土，廣告成日話撐香港人，宜家就俾個機會佢地實實際際支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>ACTION！！！請大家去Facebok page瘋狂轟炸</strong></span></span><br />\n1. Expedia: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/expedia.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexpedia.com.hk%2F&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=652a27db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/expedia.com.hk/</a><br />\n2. Trivago: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/trivagoHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FtrivagoHK%2F&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=73d224b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/trivagoHK/</a><br />\n3. Hotels. com: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Hotels.comHK/?brand_redir=180390341995122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHotels.comHK%2F%3Fbrand_redir%3D180390341995122&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=ca4544f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Hotels.comHK/?brand_redir=180390341995122</a><br />\n4. HKTV Mall: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hktvmall/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhktvmall%2F&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=4e3d52dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hktvmall/</a><br />\n5. 幸福傷風素：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFortune.Pharmacal%2F&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0doPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=3b98cf70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢啲公司燒好多錢去做social media marketing，亦都好介意網民意見，大家咁樣洗版一定有用！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請瘋狂俾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFB留言template：</span></strong><br />\nHKTV mall:<br />\n當年香港人為香港電視站出來，今天希望香港電視為香港人站出來。<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐<br />\n恥與為伍，撤回廣告<br />\n<br />\n細細聲：大家去HKTV Mall洗版嘅時候可以善意提醒下佢ztore嘅下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nExpedia:<br />\n當世道無憂時我地想去旅行會諗起expedia，希望宜家水深火熱之時expedia會支持我地。<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐<br />\n恥與為伍，撤回廣告<br />\n<br />\n幸福傷風素：<br />\n香港病了，你能令佢好番嗎？我相信你可以的<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐<br />\n恥與為伍，撤回廣告"},{"pid":"8b53a7c2ff80cec32e11094291713a62851974e7","tid":1261370,"uid":94794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:06:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65a135ff31d42d63aaba18dca93d552900acf853","tid":1261370,"uid":183890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:10:06.000Z","msg":"要唱都唱啲關事㗎啦 唔好咁幼稚"}]}